---
title: Smokey Chicken Schnitzel & Beetroot Relish with Lemon Crushed Potatoes & Apple Slaw
description: A classic schnitzel is always best served with a side of potatoes. We’re jazzing things up tonight by crushing the
potatoes with a squeeze of lemon juice. Crumb the chicken with the barbecue seasoning for a smokey flavour serve with
a sweet and vibrant beetroot relish.
